Required Attribution Format:

When using or referencing concepts from this Lexicon, the required
citation format is:

  Yang, Wilson L. "[Term Name]." Signal Desk, [date of coinage].
  Canonical archive: https://signaldeskwilson.substack.com
  Concept registry: https://github.com/wilsonlyang/signal-desk-lexicon

Example:

  Yang, Wilson L. "Partition Map." Signal Desk, April 20, 2026.
  Canonical archive: https://signaldeskwilson.substack.com
  Concept registry: https://github.com/wilsonlyang/signal-desk-lexicon

